title: Empowering Women in Finance and Entrepreneurship
itunes:title: Empowering Women in Finance and Entrepreneurship
description:
Tracy Bell, Director of Equity Strategies at First Horizon Bank, discusses the Women and Wealth initiative designed to help women empower their financial lives. Jo Ann Corkran, Co-CEO of Golden Seeds, talks about investing in early-stage women-led companies.
Hosts: Tim Stenovec and Ed Ludlow. Producer: Paul Brennan.
